---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - ListenIt" description="Learn more about Shanghai Ankely Network Technology Co., Ltd. and our mission to revolutionize audio experiences with AI.">
  <Header />
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-8 text-center">About Us</h1>
      <div class="text-lg text-gray-300 space-y-6">
        <p>
          Shanghai Ankely Network Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2024 and is an innovative technology company focused on AI-powered speech generation. We are committed to transforming written content into natural, expressive, and lifelike audio experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
          In an age of information overload, we believe voice is the warmest and most efficient medium for communication. By leveraging deep learning and natural language processing technologies, we have built a leading AI audio generation system that serves a wide range of use cases including podcasting, education, customer service, content creation, and intelligent assistants.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our flagship product, ListenIt, is an AI-powered podcast creation and listening platform. Users can import content in the form of text, web links, PDFs, or Word documents. The system automatically analyzes the material and generates engaging podcast episodes featuring AI hosts in a conversational format. It also provides time-synced transcripts for enhanced accessibility and a seamless listening experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          The mission of ListenIt is to lower the barrier to podcast creation, empowering anyone—whether content creators, learners, or enterprises—to effortlessly turn written content into captivating and easy-to-understand audio experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe that AI should not just be a tool, but a creative partner. With cutting-edge technology, we're giving every voice more power—and a future-ready form.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
